
Duild Server 
=======================


Clone this project

https://github.com/MithunTechnologiesDevOps/maven-web-application

Install maven
---------------------



FROM tomcat:8.0.20-jre8
COPY target/maven-web-application*.war /usr/local/tomcat/webapps/maven-web-application.war


Install Docker
------------------

https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/
https://get.docker.com/
for practice we can use below command 
$sudo curl -fsSL get.docker.com| /bin/bash 

ubuntu
---------
$ sudo apt install docker.io -y 

Make sure docker demon is started or not?
 $ ps -ef | grep "dockerd"

See the docker status
$ sudo service docker status

$ sudo docker version

Iam using Ubuntu user to the docker group
$ sudo usermod -aG docker ubuntu

$ exit 





linux
-------

$ sudo apt install docker.io -y 



docker build -t <Image> <Docker Build Context>

t=> tag

Command to create Docker image:
==================================

$ docker build -t naniravi/maven-web-app:1 .

.=> .Represnt Current Working Directory 





